Hi there, 

I'm Franck, and I'm an experienced driver as well as car lover since my younger age. I like beautiful cars, and always enjoy trying different type of cars ! I also travel a lot, and try to always rent cars that I've never driven before.

Today, thanks to my job, I have the opportunity to drive many high-end vehicles, and that's why I decided to share the experience with people here on Turo. Therefore I try to always offer reasonable price on our vehicle !

One of our last come in, is a brand new GMC SIERRA 4x4. The perfect vehicle to explore mountains, discover California, or just for a moving !

Don't hesitate to contact me if you have any question, or would like to rent one of our vehicle :)

Franck
